metadata.name: Fat Bonez #1
metadata.description: Fat Bonez Trademark. Fat Bonez is a Venture Backed ethereum blockchain game. There will be 4 different battles (Schedule TBA), and every group will be able to fight all 4 despite elimination. Each team will split fight winnings evenly. Group/discord username association will occur on 1/1/2023 (Discord released prior to this date). Buckle up with your group(s) and prepare for war. One of the first games connecting groups of all varities for a decentralized experience of a lifetime.
